<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Elite Watches</title>

<style>
body {
    margin:0;
    font-family:Arial;
    background:#0b0b0b;
    color:white;
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

/* HEADER */
header {
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
    background:black;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    padding:15px 20px;
    z-index:1000;
}

.logo {
    color:gold;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

nav a {
    color:white;
    margin-left:15px;
    text-decoration:none;
}
nav a:hover {color:gold;}

/* HERO */
.hero {
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px 20px;
}

.hero h1 {
    color:gold;
}

/* GRID */
.grid {
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    justify-content:center;
}

/* CARD */
.card {
    background:#1a1a1a;
    margin:15px;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:12px;
    width:250px;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
    transform:scale(1.05);
}

.card img {
    width:100%;
    border-radius:10px;
}

.price {
    color:gold;
}

/* BUTTON */
.btn {
    margin-top:10px;
    padding:10px;
    background:gold;
    border:none;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-weight:bold;
    width:100%;
}

/* BADGE */
.badge {
    position:absolute;
    margin:10px;
    background:red;
    padding:5px 8px;
    font-size:12px;
    border-radius:5px;
}

/* BLOG */
.section {
    padding:50px 20px;
    text-align:center;
}

/* FAQ */
.faq {
    max-width:700px;
    margin:auto;
    text-align:left;
}

.faq-item {
    background:#1a1a1a;
    margin:10px 0;
    padding:10px;
    border-radius:8px;
}

/* SUPPORT */
.support-btn {
    padding:12px;
    background:green;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-weight:bold;
}

/* FLOAT BUTTON */
.float-btn {
    position:fixed;
    bottom:20px;
    right:20px;
    background:gold;
    color:black;
    padding:12px 15px;
    border-radius:50px;
    font-weight:bold;
    text-decoration:none;
    z-index:999;
}

footer {
    background:black;
    text-align:center;
    padding:15px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">⌚ Elite Watches</div>
<nav>
<a href="#home">Home</a>
<a href="#blog">Blog</a>
<a href="#faq">FAQs</a>
<a href="#support">Support</a>
</nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
<h1>Luxury & Classic Watches</h1>
<p>Upgrade Your Style With Elite Watches</p>
</div>

<!-- HOME / PRODUCTS (UNCHANGED + ALL WATCHES KEPT) -->
<div class="section" id="home">

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<span class="badge">HOT</span>
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523275335684-37898b6baf30">
<h3>Luxury Gold Watch</h3>
<p class="price">Rs 4500</p>
<button class="btn" onclick="order('Luxury Gold Watch',4500)">Order Now</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<span class="badge">NEW</span>
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522312346375-d1a52e2b99b3">
<h3>Classic Leather Watch</h3>
<p class="price">Rs 2500</p>
<button class="btn" onclick="order('Classic Leather Watch',2500)">Order Now</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490367532201-b9bc1dc483f6">
<h3>Modern Black Watch</h3>
<p class="price">Rs 3500</p>
<button class="btn" onclick="order('Modern Black Watch',3500)">Order Now</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508057198894-247b23fe5ade">
<h3>Premium Silver Watch</h3>
<p class="price">Rs 4000</p>
<button class="btn" onclick="order('Premium Silver Watch',4000)">Order Now</button>
</div>

</div>
</div>

<!-- BLOG -->
<div class="section" id="blog">
<h1>📖 Blog</h1>

<p>
Watches are not just timepieces — they define personality, style, and confidence.
Luxury watches give premium feel while classic watches give simplicity.
</p>
</div>

<!-- FAQ -->
<div class="section" id="faq">
<h1>❓ FAQs</h1>

<div class="faq">

<div class="faq-item">
<b>Delivery time?</b>
<p>3–5 days all over Pakistan</p>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
<b>Payment method?</b>
<p>Cash on Delivery + WhatsApp Order</p>
</div>

<div class="faq-item">
<b>Return policy?</b>
<p>3 days checking warranty</p>
</div>

</div>
</div>

<!-- SUPPORT -->
<div class="section" id="support">
<h1>📞 Support</h1>
<p>We are available 24/7 on WhatsApp</p>

<button class="support-btn" onclick="window.open('https://wa.me/923091144241')">
WhatsApp Support
</button>
</div>

<!-- FLOAT ORDER BUTTON -->
<a class="float-btn" href="https://wa.me/923091144241">
Order Now
</a>

<footer>
© Elite Watches
</footer>

<script>
function order(name,price){
    let msg = "Order:%0A" + name + "%0APrice: Rs " + price;
    window.open("https://wa.me/923091144241?text=" + msg);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>